{"metadata":{"name":"Jami At Tirmidhi","section":{"24":"The Book on Clothing"},"section_detail":{"24":{"hadithnumber_first":1720,"hadithnumber_last":1787,"arabicnumber_first":1720,"arabicnumber_last":1787}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1787,"arabicnumber":1787,"text":"حدثنا محمد بن بشار، حدثنا معاذ بن هشام، حدثني ابي، عن قتادة، عن انس، قال كان احب الثياب الى رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم يلبسها الحبرة . قال ابو عيسى هذا حديث حسن صحيح غريب","grades":[{"name":"Ahmad Muhammad Shakir","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Bashar Awad Maarouf","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Agreed Upon"}],"reference":{"book":24,"hadith":76}}]}